-- Manchester City Beats Newcastle 2-0 to Close on League Title
-- B y   J a m e s   C o n e
-- 2012-05-06T14:24:07Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-05-06/manchester-city-beats-newcastle-2-0-to-close-on-league-title.html
Manchester City beat Newcastle 2-0 to
take a three-point lead over Manchester United atop English
soccer’s Premier League ahead of its rival’s game against
Swansea later today.  Yaya Toure got both goals in Newcastle to lift City to 86
points with one match to play. United is on 83 points with two
games remaining.  City has now won five straight matches, including a 1-0
victory against United on April 30 which took it to the top of
the standings.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
James Cone at 
 jcone@bloomberg.net  